msg: o Fixed bug in core-plugin where a map was being used and the order of object-
Classes and attributeTypes were being mangled in the generated producers.
This was resulting in unpredictable order of registration.  This was bad for
when there were dependencies between attribute types and objectClasses.
o Added code for rapidly deducing the descendants of an ancestor attributeType.
This code will be used to expand filters when general attributeTypes are used
as opposed to ones that are specific (specialized rather)
